mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest

Class AccumuloCommandLineOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest.AccumuloCommandLineOptions

  • public class AccumuloCommandLineOptions
extends Object
    This class encapsulates all of the options and parsed values specific to setting up GeoWave to appropriately connect to Accumulo. This class also can perform the function of clearing data for a namespace if that option is activated.
